### Advancia PayLedger API Tests
### Crypto & Ethereum Operations

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Get Crypto Prices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/prices
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get User Crypto Balances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/balances
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Buy Cryptocurrency
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/buy
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTC",
  "amount": "0.001",
  "fiatAmount": "100.00",
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### Sell Cryptocurrency
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/sell
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTC",
  "amount": "0.0005",
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### Get Crypto Order History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Ethereum Deposit Address
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eth/deposit-address
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Ethereum Withdraw
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/eth/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "0x742d35Cc6466C4Eb7c10e7D4A8c6e2a7b9",
  "amount": "0.1",
  "currency": "ETH"
}

###

### Get Ethereum Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eth/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Check Ethereum Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eth/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Crypto Withdrawal History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/withdrawals
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Request Crypto Withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "USDT",
  "amount": "50.00",
  "address": "0x742d35Cc6466C4Eb7c10e7D4A8c6e2a7b9",
  "network": "ETH"
}